      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW TARKOV (6) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Restricted WIN H at Geelong. Look for sharp improvement here. COME ON LARRY (1) was a little disappointing last start at Geelong when 4th (25.88) over 460m. Has won here at this journey. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from five starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. ZAMBORA BLISS (2) goes very well this trip starting four times for two wins and two minors. In the money last time at Healesville (19.85) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2.5 lengths second. Suited here and expected to run well. PAW CHRISTIE (7) pinged the lids and wasn't headed last time. Right in the mix again.",
